      "title": "Mahavidyalayam achievement in Kilinochchi Munga",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kilinochchi Mungaville Mahavidyalayam has created a historic record by securing 1st and 2nd position in the district in the engineering vocational section and 3rd and 7th position in the arts section in the results of the 2021 general education standard higher level examination.",
        "Rajasekhar Vidhusan got the first position. Selvan G. Sanojan got the second position.",
        "It is noteworthy that Jensika Sivakumar has got the 3rd position in the art category and Premkumar Kyuri has got the 7th position. (R)"
      ],
